These are Puzzles for 3x4 Level 9

.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-9-1::.
The people have 4 different hobbies: cooking, gardening, photography, skydiving
4 different brands of cigars are smoked: davidoff, fonseca, siglo, vegafina
4 different games are played: poker, chess, scrabble, bridge
 1. the person who's hobby is cooking is on the left or right of the person who's hobby is skydiving##3
 2. the person who's hobby is skydiving is on the left or right of the person who's hobby is gardening##3
 3. the person playing scrabble is not to the right of the person playing chess##8
 4. the person playing chess is not to the left of the vegafina-smoker##8
 5. the person who's hobby is cooking is in an even position##4
 6. the person who's hobby is gardening is on the right of the person playing scrabble##1
 7. the davidoff-smoker is the person playing poker##1
 8. the person playing scrabble is not the vegafina-smoker##6
 9. the person playing chess is somewhere to the right of the person who's hobby is photography##5
10. the person who's hobby is photography is not to the right of the siglo-smoker##8
11. the person who's hobby is gardening is not to the left of the person who's hobby is photography##8
12. the person playing chess is between the person who's hobby is photography and the fonseca-smoker##2
13. the person playing scrabble and the siglo-smoker have the same parity positions##9

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |       2        |     3     |    4    |
| Hobby         | photography | gardening      | skydiving | cooking |
| Job           | siglo | vegafina | fonseca      | davidoff |
| Music-Genre   | scrabble        | chess            | bridge    | poker |

