.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-9-2::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: 7up, iced-tea, milk, tea
The people use 4 different means of transport: airplane, quad-bike, roller, jet-ski
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: disaster, mystery, adventure, comedy
 1. the person driving the roller is not to the right of the person watching disaster movies##8
 2. the person drinking iced-tea is not to the right of the person drinking milk##8
 3. the person watching mystery movies and the person driving the airplane have the same parity positions##9
 4. the person driving the roller is somewhere to the right of the person driving the jet-ski##5
 5. the person watching adventure movies is on the left of the person drinking tea##1
 6. the person drinking 7up is not to the left of the person drinking iced-tea##8
 7. the person driving the jet-ski is not to the right of the person drinking tea##8
 8. the person watching mystery movies is between the person drinking iced-tea and the person drinking milk##2
 9. the person drinking 7up is on the right of the person driving the quad-bike##1
10. the person watching mystery movies is on the left of the person driving the jet-ski##1
11. the person driving the airplane is not to the left of the person watching comedy movies##8
12. the person driving the jet-ski is not to the right of the person watching disaster movies##8
13. the person driving the jet-ski is on the left of the person driving the roller##1
14. the person driving the roller is not to the left of the person drinking tea##8

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |   2   |    3     |    4    |
| Beverage      | iced-tea | 7up   | milk     | tea     |
| Music-Genre   | quad-bike    | airplane   | jet-ski      | roller    |
| Sport         | comedy   | mystery | adventure | disaster |

