.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-9-3::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: sprite, coffee, hot-chocolate, fanta
City: nizza, san-francisco, marseilles, hannover
4 different pets are kept: bird, guinea-pig, mouse, turtle
 1. the person drinking sprite is not to the left of the person traveling to nizza##8
 2. the person traveling to marseilles is on the left of the person drinking coffee##1
 3. the person traveling to marseilles is the person drinking sprite##1
 4. the person traveling to marseilles is somewhere between the person traveling to hannover and the owner of the guinea-pig##7
 5. the person drinking fanta and the person traveling to nizza have different parity positions##9
 6. the owner of the mouse is not to the right of the person drinking sprite##8
 7. the owner of the mouse is somewhere to the left of the person traveling to hannover##5
 8. the owner of the guinea-pig is somewhere to the right of the person drinking fanta##5
 9. the person traveling to san-francisco is on the left of the person traveling to nizza##1
10. the owner of the bird is between the person traveling to nizza and the owner of the turtle##2
11. the person drinking coffee is not the person traveling to nizza##6

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |     2      |    3     |    4    |
| Hobby         | fanta | hot-chocolate     | sprite  | coffee |
| Nationality   | san-francisco       | nizza    | marseilles | hannover |
| Pet           | mouse       | guinea-pig | bird     | turtle  |

