 3. the person watching thriller movies is on the right of the person watching mystery movies##1
 4. the person watching mystery movies is somewhere to the left of the owner of the hamster##5
 5. the person who's sport is rowing is on the left of the person who's sport is ice-hockey##1
 6. the person who's sport is sailing is on the left or right of the owner of the hamster##3
 7. the owner of the ferret is on the left of the owner of the hamster##1
 8. the person watching thriller movies is the person who's sport is ice-hockey##1
 9. the owner of the snake is somewhere to the left of the person watching superhero movies##5
10. the person watching thriller movies is between the person who's sport is rowing and the person watching drama movies##2
11. the owner of the snake is on the left or right of the person who's sport is lacrosse##3

.:: Answer ::.
|            |   1    |     2      |    3    |      4      |
