.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-9-20::.
There are 4 different favourite colors: apricot, turquise, pink, light-blue
4 different pets are kept: chinchilla, ferret, lizard, rabbit
The people have 4 different jobs:  mechanic, nurse, librarian, software-developer
 1. the owner of the chinchilla is on the right of the mechanic##1
 2. the librarian is on the right of the mechanic##1
 3. the nurse is not the owner of the chinchilla##6
 4. the person who likes turquise is on the right of the person who likes apricot##1
 5. the person who likes turquise is somewhere to the left of the nurse##5
 6. the person who likes apricot is somewhere to the left of the person who likes pink##5
 7. the person who likes pink and the nurse have different parity positions##9
 8. the owner of the lizard is on the left or right of the owner of the ferret##3
 9. the owner of the ferret is on the left of the mechanic##1
10. the person who likes apricot is not to the right of the person who likes turquise##8
11. the owner of the chinchilla is not the nurse##6

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |    2     |     3      |       4       |
| Nationality   | apricot | turquise    | pink   | light-blue       |
| Pet           | ferret    | lizard   | chinchilla | rabbit        |
| Sport         | software-developer  | mechanic | librarian     | nurse |

 